title: 085: Johnny Sebastian, Rob Ortiz and Breaking News!
description: In this episode Sal, Adam & Justin interview IFBB pros, Johnny Sebastian and Rob Ortiz. Not only is this episode informative and entertaining, but Johnny makes an announcement about a first in the IFBB world and you are hearing about it before ANYONE ELSE, right here on MindPump!
